{"tid":2351301,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"玩物達人●最平日租100蚊  塵封模型見光 噴油場任用","createTime":"2021-01-03T06:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T01:05:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0127f389d7ad9f05c226c1c45c28cf6e85e03c43","tid":2351301,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:13:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/tech/20210102/RHMTC4OJ4NER3I5CPTYJ2DV5XY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ftech%2F20210102%2FRHMTC4OJ4NER3I5CPTYJ2DV5XY%2F&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0F8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=379aad82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ftech%2F20210102%2FRHMTC4OJ4NER3I5CPTYJ2DV5XY%2F&h=ff01b69e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/tech/20210102/RHMTC4OJ4NER3I5CPTYJ2DV5XY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n玩物達人●最平日租100蚊 <br />\n塵封模型見光 噴油場任用<br />\n<br />\n可能因為武肺關係，近日多了人買模型，但往往只買不砌。記者決定在新一年跟模型達人學習，首次嘗試噴塗模型。講起噴油好多人都驚，一來不熟工具，二來屋企沒有適合位置。香港近年開了不少模型噴油場，今次分別帶大家到YM Studio和Hobby Field實試，教大家出街噴模型的注意事項。<br />\n<br />\n目前噴油場多數分為時租、日租、月租三種形式，時租大約$20-$40，日租約$100-$150，以新手來說，噴塗一隻1/144的模型可能要4小時以上，日租比較划算，任噴一日只是百多元，不算高消費。噴油場一般提供噴筆、泵、上色夾、切割墊等非消耗品工具，模型油、開油水等就要自備。多數噴油場也會售賣模型工具，可即場購買。<br />\n<br />\n這次找來模型達人Nic Chung教我們噴塗，首先要學的是開油，模型油一般不能直接使用，要用開油水調稀，也要準備開油樽。我們這次噴塗的是HGGTO版1/144 RX-78-2高達模型，模型油選用Mr Color的高達專用色，紅、黃、藍、白、灰五種顏色和Gaia T06-h開油水。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_ogaGTDnwfQHehXhaGxfu2reSG0=/6000x3376/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/B6UOGT5IXJEGVCJKR47BNNPJMU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_ogaGTDnwfQHehXhaGxfu2reSG0%3D%2F6000x3376%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FB6UOGT5IXJEGVCJKR47BNNPJMU.JPG&h=6a410f4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上色後的模型層次感比較豐富，比較失色的是沒有用水貼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BizPjrlyWcW5nVDxJy9Eez-CJMg=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HM6RD5AYYRA7XGIHOSTPT3LUZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBizPjrlyWcW5nVDxJy9Eez-CJMg%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHM6RD5AYYRA7XGIHOSTPT3LUZA.jpg&h=dabf47ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n模型達人Nic Chung認為，噴油時最理想是戴上防毒面罩或N95級口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4fzD7-GUyeaUSEaTKWG9a1APW8w=/1440x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AA2UPNPRTVBYZHGYLZWWVZEAAM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4fzD7-GUyeaUSEaTKWG9a1APW8w%3D%2F1440x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAA2UPNPRTVBYZHGYLZWWVZEAAM.jpg&h=94a55662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nYM Studio的美少女店員，在網上有不少人討論，studio除了賣模型，也提供噴油場租用服務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n達人教開油 噴灰左掃右要快<br />\n<br />\n「開油不是用多少開多少，通常一次要開一整瓶。」先把模型油攪勻，全數倒進開油樽，再加入開油水，要注意不同牌子的油有不同的開油比例。同樣是$18一支，Mr Color可用1:1，一份10ml的模型油加10ml的開油水；Gaia的模型油就多用1:3，比較抵用。新手不妨開口問問店員，師兄們都很樂意解答。開油後可以放幾粒玻璃珠入樽，令沉底的模型油更容易搖勻。<br />\n<br />\n模型上色前要先上底灰，「。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n底灰的度數代表幼細度，越高度數越幼滑，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n記者開始時覺得難度不低，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n噴好灰後，要等約30分鐘待模型乾透，之後就可用噴槍上色。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JOLhYehMzK59JfaIrIvUVIdH3eU=/5868x3302/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/U5HZIHWLJREV7ITFLP5VN3BFK4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJOLhYehMzK59JfaIrIvUVIdH3eU%3D%2F5868x3302%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU5HZIHWLJREV7ITFLP5VN3BFK4.JPG&h=7c33c8de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n後來記者補買兩支Modo油、滲線液、棉花棒、面相筆和模型鉗，合共約$120。<br />\n<br />\n未上色前的模型，塑膠感比較重。<br />\n未上色前的模型，塑膠感比較重。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上色三層飽和 嫌平淡可噴金屬色<br />\n<br />\n主流噴油手法是先控制出油量，薄噴一層後再大油噴第二層，多數噴。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n記者大概用了兩日，共計七個多小時完成紅、黃、藍、白、灰五色的噴塗，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n先用正黑色做底色，可以先以大油噴成亮黑光澤面，乾後再薄噴。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n本來應該7至8個小時就完成的工序，因為嘗試金屬色再加滲線和消光，總共用了。。。。。小時。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nStep 1 開油：先把模型油攪勻，再加入開油水（右），每個牌子有不同比例。<br />\nStep 1 開油：先把模型油攪勻，再加入開油水（右），每個牌子有不同比例。<br />\n<br />\nStep 2 噴灰：用噴罐手要掃得夠快，由左至右掃兩至三次，不要來回掃。<br />\nStep 2 噴灰：用噴罐手要掃得夠快，由左至右掃兩至三次，不要來回掃。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/S6j3IV5H1pjk3BtJXxrMt5szI0w=/3936x2624/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RNY5LDDJAVHHRN23W5SBASNZUM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FS6j3IV5H1pjk3BtJXxrMt5szI0w%3D%2F3936x2624%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRNY5LDDJAVHHRN23W5SBASNZUM.JPG&h=0357466b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nStep 3 上色：雙動式的噴筆比較易控制出油量和氣量。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/l0Yx9mzKdem1xcNibVKyrhhylB8=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OPOTVRA3JNE4TFVSYVAOCMPIDA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fl0Yx9mzKdem1xcNibVKyrhhylB8%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOPOTVRA3JNE4TFVSYVAOCMPIDA.jpg&h=b3dc40e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nStep 4 追加金屬色：背包用上正黑色做底再噴機械銀，噴射器直接用機械銀上色。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYM Studio<br />\n<br />\n旺角山東街47-51號中僑商業大廈1602室<br />\n<br />\nHobby Field<br />\n葵涌葵樂街裕林工業中心B座3樓B2室<br />\n<br />\n記者：司徒港燊<br />\n<br />\n攝影：鄭皓然、伍永健"},{"pid":"3ed89ac59156ee33f38a2c8da7ac6378b87e0ddd","tid":2351301,"uid":8636,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T08:33:29.000Z","msg":"Nic Chung = LS 呀風？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc149f1db723d6b370fe8a23449aa9d86f5175ef","tid":2351301,"uid":21483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T08:56:45.000Z","msg":"我估個focus 好快去咗美少女店員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b51e163dc82dda8f1ca0f2130606cfc90154d41","tid":2351301,"uid":30562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc149f1db723d6b370fe8a23449aa9d86f5175ef","tid":2351301,"uid":21483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T08:56:45.000Z","msg":"我估個focus 好快去咗美少女店員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T01:05:19.000Z","msg":"YM賣點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}